3, 185.0272, 184.7261, 185.5604, 185.1477, 185.4116, 184.6097, 183.8711, 183.8202, 184.0321, 182.4448, 181.5981, 182.0175, 181.0158, 181.4411, 180.3129, 179.3139, 180.1328, 179.096, 178.3344, 179.241, 178.8338, 176.8443, 176.5305, 177.8337, 176.7073, 177.6995, 177.4559, 177.2876, 175.9719, 172.8477, 172.7026, 174.3257, 172.4652, 168.8179, 169.3212, 166.2605, 164.9103, 168.8285, 168.9453, 168.7284, 167.3474, 169.3975, 164.5797, 165.0183, 164.3715, 163.4636, 160.8617, 165.9982, 169.6852, 167.4326, 166.7766, 170.339, 169.6567, 167.6975, 167.4576, 164.3625, 166.2866, 164.6276, 162.5368, 161.1388, 162.2638, 161.6412, 160.2236, 164.3003, 162.3729, 163.1339, 162.9683, 162.6311, 160.6916, 161.8412, 161.4922, 163.1518, 165.2454, 165.0851, 165.5844, 169.3511, 169.8332, 170.9985, 169.9965, 169.9363, 168.0453, 166.4233, 166.8615, 166.2772, 169.561], "summary_html": "<h1>盈利偏度和估值偏度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.376)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告研究了股票基本面信息偏度（盈利偏度和估值偏度）对横截面收益的预测能力。盈利偏度（如ROA/营业利润率过去8季度的偏度）正向预测收益；估值偏度（PE/POP过去252日的偏度）负向预测收益。移植到商品期货时，核心逻辑为：计算价值比（close/MA）的滚动偏度作为估值偏度的类比。低偏度品种（历史上频繁出现极端低估值）倾向于被低估，未来获得更高收益——这是基本面延迟反应和低估值风险补偿的共同结果。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3140</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.28</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.32</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.06 / 1.47</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.64</td><td>1.73</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.17</span></td><td>0.78</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.19</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.24</td><td>1.29</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td>0.11</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.57</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3142</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{val\\_ratio}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{close}_{i,t}}{\\text{MA}_{300}(\\text{close}_{i,t})}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Skew}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{T}\\sum_{s=t-T+1}^{t}\\left(\\frac{r_s - \\bar{r}}{\\hat{\\sigma}}\\right)^3, \\quad T = 252</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">r_s = \\text{val\\_ratio}_{i,s}</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\bar{r}</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}</span> 分别为窗口内的均值和标准差。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = -\\text{Skew}(\\text{val\\_ratio}_{i}, 252)</div>\n<p>负号表示低偏度品种做多、高偏度品种做空。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>首轮12变体。val_skew252_h21_raw 1.07通过，ret_skew正方向全部失败</td><td>实现核心因子：收益率偏度(4窗口)+价值比偏度(3窗口)+组合因子</td><td>Sharpe 1.066, 通过backtest gate</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>val_skew252是唯一强信号，ret_skew方向错误</td><td>翻转ret_skew方向为负；加IC gate；加180d窗口；触发cs/ts归一化</td><td>Sharpe 1.133 (cs版提升)。IC gate无效（被dedup）</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>需优化MA分母和skew窗口；val_skew252是核心</td><td>参数网格：MA{200,252,300} x Skew{200,252,300} x Hold{10,21}；加hold 10d</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.376</strong>。MA300+Skew252+Hold10为最优组合</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R3 中将 hold_days 从 21 缩短至 10 是最大提升来源（1.07 -&gt; 1.38），因为偏度信号衰减较快，短持仓更好捕捉均值回复效应。MA300（vs 252）使价值比分母更平滑，减少噪声。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（69个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>信号逻辑</strong>: 截面因子，低偏度品种做多/高偏度品种做空</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 原报告为股票因子，移植到商品期货时盈利偏度（收益率偏度）效果较弱，估值偏度（价值比偏度）是主要alpha来源。短窗口skew（&lt;120d）和长hold（&gt;21d）效果较差。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MA_W</code></td><td><code>300</code></td><td>MA window for value ratio</td></tr><tr><td><code>SKEW_W</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>skewness window</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>DIRECTION</code></td><td><code>-1.0</code></td><td>low skew = bullish</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9953</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.19s</li>\n</ul>"}